/// <para>   - Default to ImGuiTableFlags_SizingFixedFit    if ScrollX is on, or if host window has ImGuiWindowFlags_AlwaysAutoResize.</para>
/// <para>   - Default to ImGuiTableFlags_SizingStretchSame if ScrollX is off.</para>
